description: "Map of the Moluccas (Maluku Islands) divided into the residencies of Ternate (orange borders) and Ambon (green borders). Many place names are in Dutch and Malay, and there is an inset map of the city of Ambon. Timor is marked as Portuguese territory."
title: "Kaart der Molukken. [Inset] Ambon en Omstreken at 1:20,000 [cartographic material]"
